title: Eleven People Arrested during Motorcycle Gathering - Hoffman Ave., Lindenhurst... (Suffolk County Police Department)
text: ( Source : Suffolk County Police Department ) The Suffolk County Police Department have arrested 11 people and recovered numerous weapons, drugs and vehicles during a gathering hosted by the Pagan Motorcycle Club in Lindenhurst yesterday.
